HEADWORD: Pessulus
<hw>Pes"su*lus</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Pessuli</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[L., a bolt.]</ety>
<fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>A delicate bar of cartilage connecting the
dorsal and ventral extremities of the first pair of bronchial cartilages
in the syrinx of birds.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

